data.title: 2nd Battalion, Royal Australian Regiment
data.meta_description: The 2nd Battalion, Royal Australian Regiment is an amphibious light infantry battalion of the Australian Army part of the 1st Division Amphibious Task Group based at Lavarack Barracks in Townsville.
data.text:
For 2 RAR (Rhodesian), see Rhodesian African Rifles.

For other uses, see 2nd Battalion (Australia) and 2/2nd Battalion (Australia).

The 2nd Battalion, Royal Australian Regiment (2 RAR) is an amphibious light infantry battalion of the Australian Army part of the 1st Division Amphibious Task Group based at Lavarack Barracks in Townsville.
